sentences.sentence: This paper proposes a new linear modeling of intercell joint resource allocation, based on multicell centralized scheduling.
sentences.translation: 文章提出了一种基于多小区集中式调度方案基础上的小区间联合资源分配的线性建模方法。

sentences.sentence: In this paper we have described a Complementary Multicell-type Logic Circuit which is based on CMOS and linear IC technology.
sentences.translation: 本文提出了一种基于CMOS和线性IC工艺的互补多元逻辑电路。
